Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fs42\fad(300,300)}{\move(720,60,720,8)}{\blur3}字幕重校、压制：巴洛克哥特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经把知道的全都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}十分抱歉 这是阿切尔中佐的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开什么玩笑 我这正急着有事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎 红莲之炼金术师扎尔夫·J·金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有缀命之炼金术师肖·塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我遵守了约定 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用害怕 我会保障你的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以我法兰克·阿切尔的名义保证
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安…安全?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:00:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 你将回到军队中继续进行研究
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}作为我的直属部下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能够继续…进行研究?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}改变作战指令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对反抗的人不用留情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.08,0:01:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把盘踞在这店里的危险分子全部除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 这样做可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要有了塔克 那种程度的家伙无论多少都能造得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}格利德 我只要有它你就无法出手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人没有什么牺牲的话就什么都得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了得到什么东西就需要付出同等的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是炼金术的等价交换原则
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时我们坚信那就是世界的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fn华康雅艺体W6\pos(720,760)\3c&HD3CF9C&\fs70}贪欲的理论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}混账
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}格利德 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎…怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我名乃阿莱克斯·鲁伊·阿姆斯特朗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人称豪腕之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请交还 阿尔方斯·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 斯洛斯那家伙真会支使人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 让那家伙逃了有我的责任 也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 怎么办呢 格利德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是我阿姆斯特朗家代代相传的艺术炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看来普通的办法是对付不了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要来真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好可怕的形貌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好久没这么热血沸腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真不愧是阿姆斯特朗少佐 豪腕不减当年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也作为一名士兵参加了伊修巴尔歼灭战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}过去的战友么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我就更不愿杀你了 投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恕难从命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐 请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要白白送命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我们就听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告诉金布利和塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这次厚礼我必定奉还
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还真是安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚才还那么大吵大闹来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概喊累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对我们来说这真是谢天谢地了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那倒也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到最后逃出来的只有我们几个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下来要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还打算东逃西窜到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过我想那也为时已晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你和格拉特尼已经见过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}初次见面 我是现在的拉斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我直说了 格利德 现在有两条路让你选
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要么再次被封印 要么命丧于此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道我会干掉吗  被你？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身为人造人却违抗那一位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在140年前被封印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那一位生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也该完了吧 格利德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完了 完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 小子 请你协助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛蒂尔就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}罗阿先生 道尔切特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等 等等 发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走 格利德 这儿交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们不能在这里失去您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为大家报仇的事 就交给您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}养了些很忠实的部下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我被与狗合成在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忠心耿耿是狗的秉性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不准再向前一步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}格利德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}逃也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}害怕的话夹起尾巴逃走就好了 道尔切特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我倒是想呢 不过我没那个能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没关系么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事到如今还说这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是…但丁夫人家的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 你还真是个好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那儿变成那样 不正好是逃跑的机会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使那么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛蒂尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早上之前就那样呆在里边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果那之后我还没有回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就一个人逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}格利德 您究竟要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思了 小子 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放我出来 给我打开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行 格利德先生说了不能出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结果还是回到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知为何脚就朝这儿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道是想向那家伙乞求饶命么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是乖孩子啊 格利德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样事情就照那一位所想的进行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 这么一来我们的工作就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肚子又饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你来这里的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因为这里是你出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是什么人 从但丁那里都听说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但丁夫人的话 在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可能…就凭你这种小丫头 不可能做到这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你究竟是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生命…我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到你了 格利德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但丁夫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}格利德 你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道 我还想问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我倒是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你为什么如此想救弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔他是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做好准备了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔他在哪儿 快把他还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想让我还给你的话…你该明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了 你的准备只有这种程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来修正我吧 我不是个"错误"么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前我也说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果想打倒我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就怀着对你的杀心…对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真不愧是我的整备师 都成了这副模样居然还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可是一点都不疼不痒 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这次到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你对我的盾做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想想看其实很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从无不可能生出有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是说你那盾是从身体中什么地方变化出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是人造人 身体的组成成份也跟人是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人体中能转化为硬度高且耐磨的物质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是占人体三分之一的碳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根据碳原子空间排列的不同 其硬度会发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因此它可以组成从石墨到金刚石等一系列物质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明白了这点 接下来就是我的专长了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还没有输
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胜负已分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听你弟弟说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可是不死之身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么就只好打到你说为止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啊 不这样就太无趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不愧是我看中的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不简…单嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔呢 阿尔在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我早就把他放了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}格利德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人造人是你们炼金术师进行人体炼成时诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们在那个要被复活的人的骨头前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就无法活动自如了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是人造人的…弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么 为什么要告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能够打倒她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经不想再被封印了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}格利德 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可是"贪欲" 所以我的生命也必须随我的喜好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}格利德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把它们…毁掉…拜托…你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会吧…格利德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在干什么 开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是脑袋掉了都不会死的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}格利德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛蒂尔小姐…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}师父为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道 我赶来的时候已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}莱拉也不知去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}师父 真的很抱歉 我们要去伊修巴尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再留在师父身边 也只是给您添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}师父可能也被军队盯上了 能不能暂时躲躲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 还要你们来担心我 我也太惨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无论如何都要走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不论发生了什么 我们都要继续我们的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直到取回自己的身体为止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他日再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.24,0:23:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第三十五集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愚者的再会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.47,0:23:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们来自何方又将去往何处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是愚蠢之人的疑问吗
